---
title: Sheet Pan Chicken and Veggies with Garlicky Pan Gravy
description: Fall favourites combine in one easy sheet-pan dinner extravaganza! Roasted apples, squash and red onion form the base for succulent chicken. A sprinkling of nuts and cranberries ties this sweet-savoury dinner together!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/farmers-market-chicken-745f642c.jpg
